basic triangle perimeter sum of two sides should be greater than the third side.*

*Sort array in decreasing order to calculate maximum possible perimeter
we iterate to nums.size()-2 cause we need 3 no's*

*Checking the three nos from ith posn i.e nums at* i, i+1, i+2 *if they fulfill triangles perimeter property they are good to go
so we return the sum of the 3no's.*

